[Plague, caused by _Yersinia pestis_ is a reportable disease. Physicians
should report it to the proper health authorities, probably the state
health department. Veterinarians are reminded it is a reportable disease
and should be reported to the state health departments. It is a preventable
disease in pets. People with pets should exercise pest control measures in
the home and yard and seek veterinary help to control/rid fleas from pets.
